## Introduction:

Welcome to the DotpotiT Admin App! This is the admin-side application of DotpotiT, which provides an efficient and user-friendly interface for managing Dotpot iT official website. This README.md file provides information on how to set up and deploy the admin app on Vercel.

## Features:

- User-friendly interface with modern design
- Secure API for efficient and secure data storage and management
- A responsive design that adapts to various screen sizes
- A portfolio section that showcases the company's previous projects
- A contact section that allows users to get in touch with the company
- A Blog section that allows creating and editing blog articles.
- Company Info Management.
- Company Services and Products Management.
- Order Management.
- Job portal management.
- Website Theme management.

## Technologies Used

- NodeJs
- React Vite
- MongoDB
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios

## Installation
### Follow these steps to install and run the admin app:

- Make sure you have Git and Node.js installed on your computer.

- Clone the repository by running the following command in your terminal:

```git clone https://github.com/DotpotiT/Admin.git```

- Open the downloaded 'Admin' folder in your preferred IDE (e.g., VSCode).

- Open a terminal in the 'admin' directory:

- Install the dependencies by running the following command:

`npm install`

- Start the development server by running the following command:

```npm run dev```

The admin app will be running on http://localhost:5173.

## Deployment on Vercel
To deploy the admin app on Vercel, follow these steps:

- Make sure you have a Vercel account. If you don't, you can sign up at https://vercel.com.
- Go to [Vercel Dashboard](https://vercel.com/dashboard).
- Go to Add New Project.
- From the dropdown select Add Github Account.
- Import the project you want to deploy.
- Give a project name.
- Hit Deploy. And deployment of the project will be done.
- Now Copy the [Domain Name](https://admin-red-xi.vercel.app) and open it in your browser.

Now you can use your Admin app using this domain.

